"}\n"
"```"

#: src/language/supported-features.md:19
msgid "All primitives are represented as 64-bit NaN-boxed values at runtime."
msgstr ""
"Alle Primitiven werden zur Laufzeit als 64-Bit-NaN-geboxte Werte "
