msgstr "`Shell_NotifyIconW` + `TrackPopupMenu`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:69
msgid ""
"Icon appears in the notification area (bottom-right). Left-click → `onClick`"
" callback. Right-click → menu. PNG and `.ico` paths supported (PNG via "
"`LoadImageW` with `LR_LOADFROMFILE`). `trayCreate` must come after "
"`App({...})` since the tray reuses the main window's `WndProc`."
msgstr ""
"Das Icon erscheint im Benachrichtigungsbereich (unten rechts). Linksklick → "
"`onClick`-Callback. Rechtsklick → Menü. PNG- und `.ico`-Pfade unterstützt "
"(PNG via `LoadImageW` mit `LR_LOADFROMFILE`). `trayCreate` muss nach "
"`App({...})` kommen, da der Tray die `WndProc` des Hauptfensters "
"wiederverwendet."

