msgstr "Unterstützte Pakete"

#: src/stdlib/overview.md:22
msgid "Networking & HTTP"
msgstr "Netzwerk & HTTP"

#: src/stdlib/overview.md:23
msgid ""
"**node:http** / **node:https** / **node:http2** — Node.js stdlib HTTP server"
" modules + WebSocket upgrade dispatch (issue #577). The full "
"`IncomingMessage` / `ServerResponse` surface plus TLS via rustls and HTTP/2 "
"via ALPN. See [HTTP & Networking](http.md#nodejs-compatibility--nodehttp--"
"nodehttps--nodehttp2)."
msgstr ""
"**node:http** / **node:https** / **node:http2** — Node.js-stdlib-HTTP-"
"Server-Module + WebSocket-Upgrade-Dispatch (Issue #577). Die vollständige "
"`IncomingMessage`- / `ServerResponse`-Oberfläche plus TLS via rustls und "
"HTTP/2 via ALPN. Siehe [HTTP & Netzwerk](http.md#nodejs-compatibility--"
"nodehttp--nodehttps--nodehttp2)."

