#: src/stdlib/http.md:385
msgid ""
"The full SigV4 signing chain (Web Crypto HMAC-SHA-256 + SHA-256, "
"TextEncoder, URLSearchParams, Headers iteration, typed-array byte "
"marshalling) is exercised end-to-end. Read paths (`getObject`, `statObject`,"
" `deleteObject`, `listObjects`, `presignedGetObject`, `presignedPostObject`)"
" are verified byte-identical to `bun` against pinned test vectors and will "
"authenticate against real S3."
msgstr ""
"Die vollständige SigV4-Signaturkette (Web Crypto HMAC-SHA-256 + SHA-256, "
"TextEncoder, URLSearchParams, Headers-Iteration, Typed-Array-Byte-"
"Marshalling) wird durchgängig ausgeübt. Read-Pfade (`getObject`, "
"`statObject`, `deleteObject`, `listObjects`, `presignedGetObject`, "
"`presignedPostObject`) sind byte-identisch zu `bun` gegen gepinnte Test-"
"Vektoren verifiziert und werden gegen echtes S3 authentifizieren."

#: src/stdlib/http.md:387
msgid ""
"Multipart uploads (`putObject` with a `ReadableStream` source large enough "
"to chunk) exercise additional surface — `WritableStream` / `TransformStream`"
" subclassing per #562 — that path compiles but isn't independently verified "
"against pinned vectors here."
msgstr ""
"Multipart-Uploads (`putObject` mit einer `ReadableStream`-Quelle, die groß "
"genug zum Chunken ist) trainieren zusätzliche Oberfläche — `WritableStream`-"
" / `TransformStream`-Subclassing per #562 — dieser Pfad kompiliert, ist aber"
" hier nicht unabhängig gegen gepinnte Vektoren verifiziert."

#: src/stdlib/http.md:389
msgid ""
"For the AWS SDK v3 (`@aws-sdk/client-s3`): Perry currently can't compile it."
" Its dependency tree pulls in `@smithy/*` and runtime middleware "
"registration that uses `Proxy` and dynamic property assignment, neither of "
"which is in Perry's [TypeScript subset](../language/limitations.md). "
"`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client` covers the same surface "
"(Put/Get/Head/Delete/List/presign + multipart) for almost every real-world "
"need."
msgstr ""
"Für das AWS SDK v3 (`@aws-sdk/client-s3`): Perry kann es derzeit nicht "
"kompilieren. Sein Abhängigkeitsbaum zieht `@smithy/*` und Runtime-"
"Middleware-Registrierung herein, die `Proxy` und dynamische Eigenschafts-"
"Zuweisung verwenden, von denen keines in Perrys [TypeScript-"
"Subset](../language/limitations.md) enthalten ist. "
"`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client` deckt dieselbe Oberfläche "
"(Put/Get/Head/Delete/List/presign + Multipart) für fast jeden realen Bedarf "
"ab."

#: src/stdlib/database.md:3
