#: src/container/containers.md:67
msgid ""
"For an untrusted workload (e.g. running user-supplied code, executing a "
"build script from an untrusted source) the recommended starting point is "
"\"drop everything, add back what you need\":"
msgstr ""
"Für einen nicht vertrauenswürdigen Workload (z. B. Ausführung von vom "
