msgid "Workload-graph policy tiers (`perry/workloads`)"
msgstr "Workload-Graph-Richtlinienebenen (`perry/workloads`)"

#: src/container/security.md:147
msgid ""
"For multi-node deployments where different workloads have different trust "
"levels, the workload-graph engine accepts a per-node `policy`:"
msgstr ""
"Für Multi-Node-Deployments, bei denen verschiedene Workloads "
"unterschiedliche Vertrauensstufen haben, akzeptiert die Workload-Graph-"
"Engine eine knotenspezifische `policy`:"

#: src/container/security.md:150
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { graph, runGraph, runtime, policy } from \"perry/workloads\";\n"
"\n"
"const g = graph(\"my-app\", {\n"
"  trusted_db:    { image: \"postgres:16-alpine\",\n"
"                   runtime: runtime.oci(),\n"
"                   policy:  policy.default() },        // no extra hardening\n"
"\n"
"  isolated_api:  { image: \"myapp/api\",\n"
"                   runtime: runtime.oci(),\n"
"                   policy:  policy.isolated() },       // no_network=true\n"
"\n"
"  hardened_proxy: { image: \"myapp/proxy\",\n"
"                    runtime: runtime.oci(),\n"
"                    policy:  policy.hardened() },      // read_only_root + seccomp\n"
"\n"
"  untrusted_eval: { image: \"myapp/sandbox\",\n"
"                    runtime: runtime.microvm(),         // ← required by tier\n"
"                    policy:  policy.untrusted() },     // microVM-only, all hardening on\n"
"});\n"
"\n"
"await runGraph(g);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/container/security.md:174
