#: src/cli/perry-toml.md:202
msgid ""
"**`\"appstore\"`** — Signs with an App Store distribution certificate and "
"uploads to App Store Connect. Requires `team_id`, `key_id`, `issuer_id`, and"
" `p8_key_path`."
msgstr ""
